Name: Dimension Observer
Desc: Each swap has a 20% chance to increase the score of a random color orb pinged by 20%.

Name: Puppet Theater
Desc: Each swap has a 40% chance to ping 1 random orb.

Name: Blade of History
Desc: Orbs pinged with items give 150% score.

Name: Lightning Fall
Desc: Each swap ping has a 15% chance to make the pinging score critical (x200%).

Name: Echoing Twins
Desc: Basic Attack Orbs' chance to appear increases by 5%
